Setup
-----
1. run "lein deps"


Starting a cluster
------------------

Set number of supervisor nodes you want in conf/clusters.yaml. In conf/storm.yaml you can override/add configurations for storm. Then run:

lein run :deploy --start --name mystormcluster

You can have multiple storm clusters under different "--name". If you leave out the --name parameter, the name defaults to "dev"


Stopping a cluster
-------------------

lein run :deploy --stop --name mystormcluster




